OL,3,C'Physical threat' from Iran has
OL,4,C'increased significantly', watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe threat of physical attacks on
OL,8,Fpeople living in the UK by Iran has
OL,9,Fincreased "significantly" since 2022,
OL,10,FParliament's intelligence watchdog has
OL,11,Fwarned.
OL,13,FIn a report published on Thursday,
OL,14,FParliament's Intelligence and Security
OL,15,FCommittee described the threat from
OL,16,FIran as "persistent" and
OL,17,F"unpredictable".
