OL,3,C'Physical threat' from Iran has
OL,4,C'increased significantly', watchdog
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe committee found the "physical
OL,8,Fthreat" from Iran had "significantly
OL,9,Fincreased", focused on Iranian
OL,10,Fdissidents and Israeli interets, and
OL,11,Fwas now "comparable with the threat
OL,12,Fposed by Russia".
OL,14,FIt also warned that the nuclear threat
OL,15,Ffrom Iran had also increased, since
OL,16,Fthe US withdrew from the international
OL,17,Fnuclear agreement in 2018, and argued
OL,18,Fthat de-escalation "must be a
OL,19,Fpriority".
