OL,7,FThe committee has urged the government
OL,8,Fto make clear to Iran that attempts
OL,9,Fwould "constitute an attack on the UK
OL,10,Fand would receive the appropriate
OL,11,Fresponse".
OL,13,FCommittee chairman Lord Beamish said:
OL,14,F"Iran poses a wide-ranging, persistent
OL,15,Fand unpredictable threat to the UK, UK
OL,16,Fnationals and UK interests".
