OL,7,FDescribing Iran's "high appetite for
OL,8,Frisk when conducting offensive
OL,9,Factivity", he added: "As the committee
OL,10,Fwas told, Iran is there across the
OL,11,Ffull spectrum of all the kinds of
OL,12,Fthreats we have to be concerned with."
OL,14,FHis committee also recommended that
OL,15,Fthe Government consider whether it was
OL,16,F"legally possible and practicable" to
OL,17,Fproscribe Iran's Islamic Revolutionary
OL,18,FGuard Corps (IRGC) as a terrorist
OL,19,Forganisation and make a full statement
OL,20,Fto Parliament on the issue.
