OL,7,FMinisters have faced calls in recent
OL,8,Fyears to ban the IRGC, but the
OL,9,Fcommittee recognised there were
OL,10,F"complexities inherent" in such a
OL,11,Fdecision.
OL,13,FSince August 2023, the international
OL,14,Fpicture has changed with the outbreak
OL,15,Fof the Israel-Gaza war and the US
OL,16,Fstrikes on Irans's nuclear targets.
OL,18,FDespite these changes, the committee
OL,19,Finsisted its recommendations remained
OL,20,F"relevant".
