OL,7,FThe committee warned that, while Iran
OL,8,Fhad neither developed a nuclear weapon
OL,9,Fnor decided to produce one by August
OL,10,F2023, it had taken steps towards
OL,11,Fdevelopment in recent years since
OL,12,FDonald Trump withdrew from the 2018
OL,13,Fdeal.
OL,15,FIt also warned that the UK remained a
OL,16,Ftarget for Iranian espionage, which it
OL,17,Ffound was "narrower in scope and
OL,18,Fscale" and "less sophisticated" than
OL,19,Fthe threat from Russia and China.
